      <h3>Investing Methods</h3>
      <p class="module-desc">Choosing the right path for your specific financial goals.</p>
      <div class="card-divider"></div>
      <ul class="topic-list">
        <li><a href="/learn/sip-deep-dive"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right chevron"></i>SIP – Deep Dive</a></li>
        <li><a href="/learn/lumpsum"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right chevron"></i>Lumpsum Strategy</a></li>
        <li><a href="/learn/swp"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right chevron"></i>Retiring with SWP</a></li>
