      <p class="module-desc">Understanding volatility and why FD isn't always "safe."</p>
      <div class="card-divider"></div>
      <ul class="topic-list">
        <li><a href="/learn/risk-volatility"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right chevron"></i>Market Risk vs Volatility</a></li>
        <li><a href="/learn/inflation"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right chevron"></i>The Silent Wealth Killer</a></li>
        <li><a href="/learn/fd-vs-mutual-fund"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right chevron"></i>FD vs Mutual Funds</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Module 04 -->
    <div class="module-card">
      <span class="module-number">Module 04</span>
      <h3>Long-Term Thinking</h3>
      <p class="module-desc">The psychology of money and the magic of compounding.</p>
      <div class="card-divider"></div>
      <ul class="topic-list">
        <li><a href="/learn/compounding"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right chevron"></i>Compounding Math</a></li>
        <li><a href="/learn/time-in-market"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right chevron"></i>Time in the Market</a></li>
        <li><a href="/learn/tax-planning"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right chevron"></i>Tax Planning & Efficiency</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Module 05 -->
    <div class="module-card">
      <span class="module-number">Module 05</span>
      <h3>Protection & Optimization</h3>
      <p class="module-desc">Protect and grow what you've already built.</p>
      <div class="card-divider"></div>
      <ul class="topic-list">
        <li><a href="/learn/insurance-basics"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right chevron"></i>Insurance Basics</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- AI TUTOR BANNER -->
  <div class="assistant-banner">
    <div class="assistant-icon-wrap">
      <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="assistant-text">
      <h4>Need a personal tutor?</h4>
      <p>Each topic includes an AI Learning Assistant to explain concepts with simple, real-world examples. Click on any topic to start.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</main>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>
